title: Puerto Ricans in Paris| Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 13
description:
WELCOME to Chrissy Chaos! 


This episode Chrissy Chaos talks about his upcoming baby and how the his kid can't spell. What are top cities for plastic surgery? Who gets the most plastic surgery done white women? ANXIETY TUESDAY IS ABOUT HIKING TODAY! Ever throw up on a hike?! How do you survive lost in the woods?! Vin and Chris went to Paris and things get WILD. Vin talks what it's like to be in Paris with Chris.....TI TI JERRY answers some mail from the fans! Will she chop off her WEE WEE?! Chris answers a few video questions from the fans. If you want to send us a video question email us at chrissychaospodcast@gmail.com When did you fall out of love with sports? What's the sexiest learning disability? Chris talks about how awkward it can get with a new girlfriends parents. 48 laws of power time!!!! Poop fingers are the ultimate defense. Vin and Chris talk about bar fights. Shout out Brendan Schaub and Ghost Adventures! Chrissy talks about the Catacombs of Paris. Even Elon Musk is afraid of his baby mamma. Shout out Nate Bargatze! Homelesspimp talks about the insane thing that happened while Netflix was taping Nate's special.


Remember to rate us on iTunes and Join our Patreon for a WEEKLY bonus ep!
